It may be one of the most iconic shots in the musical history, but Abbey Road has left visitors to the scene somewhat disappointed. 

Hilarious TripAdvisor reviews show how the world's most famous zebra crossing has even been slammed as 'just a street'.

The Abbey Road crossing became a must-see site for fans after The Beatles were snapped walking across it for the cover of their 11th studio album.

